pt in regards to risk/time vs reward.<br>
<br>
How it works is simple.<br>
<br>
Every x minutes or seconds (i dont have the time offhand), 3 skeletons spawn.  These can be normal (sk) skels, 'priest' skels, or a low end boss.  These low end bosses are very easy, and appear to have the 'battle' prefix.<br>
<br>
Now every 30-45 minutes, a decent boss will spawn, near the warder and walk in all alone.  These bosses tend to have 'war' prefix aka warlord, warmonger etc.  I believe these are also random, but I can't say for sure.<br>
<br>
